data.description: Spacious home with many nice features in NaplesFL !  4 bedrooms plus family room and living room, open patio and fenced yard, new roof in 2013, new ac equipment in 2013, tile flooring, 2 car attached garage, convenient location not far from Santa Barbara.  Move in condition. Owner is finishing the master bathroom upgrade. See the pictures and you'll see the lovely kitchen, nice décor, spacious rooms. Agents: Survey and elevation cert attached. Great back yard !
